The paper also mentions the use of extension fields, which are commonly studied in the subfield of Information Theory (cs.IT). The paper also mentions the use of finite fields, which is a topic studied in the subfield of Cybersecurity (cs.CY). Finally, the paper discusses the construction of new protocols, which is a topic studied in the subfield of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
